title: Ep. - 406 - JED WYATT FROM THE BACHELORETTE
description:
Kate talks about her question at the Real Housewives of Beverly Hills reunion, Found on Netflix, and

 

Jed Wyatt appeared in season 15 of The Bachelorette. He was Hannah Brown’s final choice, but ultimately the couple ended their engagement months after the show ended. Jed discusses the fallout from the breakup including his own mental health, and how the show changed the course of his life. He is a musician now living in Nashville, Tennessee.
